00:00:02.199 --> 00:00:08.849
In this video you will learn :
How to add social media buttons to YouTube

00:00:08.849 --> 00:00:11.030
Channel, Like twitter facebook instagram..

00:00:11.030 --> 00:00:16.550
Step 1.
Go to YouTube channel Page and click the edit

00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:20.020
button on upper right corner of Channel art
section.

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:25.710
Step 2:
Now you will see two options 1. Edit Link

00:00:25.710 --> 00:00:30.980
2.Edit Channel Art
click on edit link

00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:37.680
Now at the bottom of the new page you will
find Custom Link and Add button

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:44.680
Step 3:
Click on Add button, now two small tabs write

00:00:45.460 --> 00:00:48.850
the name of media button or webpage and in
url tab write or paste the link.

00:00:48.850 --> 00:00:55.850
For example if you want to add twitter button
, write twitter in first tab and paste your

00:00:56.300 --> 00:01:03.300
twitter link in second. for twitter link log
in to your twitter page 
and copy the url containing your username.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:44.200
now paste it in the tab.
to add any webpage or your own website link,

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:14.119
type the name of website in first tab and
type the url of the website in url tab...click

00:02:40.510 --> 00:02:42.780
the done button.

00:02:42.780 --> 00:02:49.780
now you can see social media buttons in Your youtube channel ... 

